<br>
An ex of mine from a few years ago was very into RPGs. He had a weekly gaming group and had been playing, much to his family's dismay, for over 10 years. They (mother and 2 sisters) did everything they could to try to dissuade him and belittle him for it. Every referance about him &quot;playing those games&quot; was done in a clearly demeaning manner, even moreso around his friends. (All of which happened to be gamers themselves, so their attempts to embarass him that way just ended up irritating people.) <br>
<br>
